.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45349498e8dac6933bb7268e8172ee8342028563","tid":2494894,"uid":45003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4500cb1bcd6182e36774bc5109cefc47892e4865","tid":2494894,"uid":245849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7049258e8a86479f4e839d4b0afe7abb2b8def7d","tid":2494894,"uid":113183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:14:55.000Z","msg":"第時香港都係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:27:53.000Z","msg":"已經開始緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T23:29:33.000Z","msg":"重講第時 一年一度國安教育日都搞咗一次啦"},{"pid":"7be562ddcff111b7daca7409d72eb355324c4dcc","tid":2494894,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"276a61104a0fe2b9c5fe2f133052ea10bd7446e6","tid":2494894,"uid":278298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T00:58:45.000Z","msg":"俄佬同isis只有一綫之差"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T23:40:50.000Z","msg":"普京=現代可汗 有13世紀中意向外侵略嘅性格"}]}